  "page": {
    "documentTitle": "滿意化 | Concept Reading Lab",
    "bodyClass": "knowledge-page knowledge-satisficing",
    "heroHtml": "<div class=\"hero-inner\">\n  <div>\n    <p class=\"kicker\">Knowledge Study / decision / enough / progress</p>\n    <h1>滿意化</h1>\n    <p class=\"topic-subtitle\">Satisficing</p>\n    <p class=\"thesis\">在資訊有限、時間有限、注意力有限的現實裡，很多時候與其追最優，不如先找到足夠好的解，讓系統繼續前進。</p>\n    <div class=\"hero-prompt\">\n      <strong>Read For</strong>\n      <p>這一頁要把『不夠完美』和『在現實限制下已足夠合理』拆開，因為很多卡住不是因為標準太高，而是忘了搜尋本身也有成本。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <aside class=\"hero-note\" aria-label=\"主題資訊\">\n    <dl class=\"lexical-meta lexical-meta--knowledge\" aria-label=\"主題摘要\">\n      <div>\n        <dt>主題類型</dt>\n        <dd>決策策略 / 有限理性</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>核心問題</dt>\n        <dd>Choosing an option that is good enough rather than globally optimal</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>主要判準</dt>\n        <dd>搜尋成本、最低門檻、最優幻覺、行動速度</dd>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <dt>讀完產出</dt>\n        <dd>能更清楚地在需要最優與只需夠好的場景之間做區分</dd>\n      </div>\n    </dl>\n    <div class=\"knowledge-map\" aria-label=\"閱讀結構示意\">\n      <span>有限</span>\n      <span>夠好</span>\n      <span>前進</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n</div>",
    "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"compass\" aria-label=\"頁內導覽\">\n  <span>Reading Path</span>\n  <a href=\"#core\">讀法總覽</a>\n  <a href=\"#setup\">問題設定</a>\n  <a href=\"#lenses\">判準透鏡</a>\n  <a href=\"#psychology\">心理連結</a>\n  <a href=\"#applications\">現實映射</a>\n  <a href=\"#misreadings\">誤讀校正</a>\n  <a href=\"#questions\">延伸提問</a>\n  <a href=\"#sources\">來源</a>\n</aside>\n\n<article class=\"article\">\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"core\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Orientation</p>\n      <h2>不是每一題都值得找到全域最優，有些題目最重要的是不要把自己困死在搜尋裡</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">滿意化是有限理性的成熟策略，不是偷懶版本的理性。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"core-card\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Core Tension</p>\n      <p>追最優能提升品質，但如果搜尋成本高到吞掉行動機會，最優追求本身就會開始不划算。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"principle-strip\" aria-label=\"本頁讀法\">\n      <div>\n        <span>01</span>\n        <strong>先定最低可接受門檻</strong>\n        <p>沒有門檻就容易在選項海裡一直漂。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>02</span>\n        <strong>再把搜尋成本算進來</strong>\n        <p>多比較一輪不是免費，它會消耗時間與注意力。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <span>03</span>\n        <strong>最後區分高風險與低風險場景</strong>\n        <p>不是所有題目都適合滿意化，但很多日常題目很適合。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"setup\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Setup</p>\n      <h2>從一個你一直想找到最好，結果遲遲沒辦法開始的選擇開始</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">滿意化特別適合資源有限、可逆性中等、選項很多的現實情境。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>最小劇情</strong>\n        <p>你一直想選最理想的工具鏈，結果比較了很久仍無法開始；其實一套符合關鍵條件、可日後再調的方案已足夠推進工作。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tile\">\n        <strong>真正難點</strong>\n        <p>真正要接受的不是品質變差，而是有些題目的最優資訊永遠拿不到。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"concept-flow\" aria-label=\"問題展開\">\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">搜尋空間很大</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">最優追求成本持續上升</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-step\">改用足夠好門檻讓決策前進</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"paradox-frame\">\n      <strong>Key Point</strong>\n      <p>滿意化最有用的地方，是把有限理性從缺陷翻成策略。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"lenses\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Lenses</p>\n      <h2>四個看夠好策略的角度</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">要用得好，關鍵不是降低標準，而是知道哪個標準是此刻最值得守的。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"lens-grid\">\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>門檻清晰度</strong>\n        <p>你知道什麼叫夠好嗎，還是只是隨便接受？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>可逆性</strong>\n        <p>選錯後是否還有調整空間？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>搜尋成本</strong>\n        <p>再花一輪找更好，值得嗎？</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"lens-card\">\n        <strong>風險後果</strong>\n        <p>這是能先前進再迭代的題，還是一次選錯代價很高的題？</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>情境</th>\n            <th>追最優的代價</th>\n            <th>滿意化能提供什麼</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>工具選型</td>\n            <td>比較時間吞掉開工時機</td>\n            <td>先用符合核心需求者上手</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>招聘初篩</td>\n            <td>每位都要最完整比較很慢</td>\n            <td>先用最低門檻過濾再深入</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>專案決策</td>\n            <td>想找完美方案導致停滯</td>\n            <td>先選足以安全前進的路徑</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"psychology\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Psychology</p>\n      <h2>為什麼人有時寧願卡住也不願接受夠好</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">因為『夠好』常被誤讀成將就，而『最優』則帶著一種道德上的高標幻覺。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>最優承諾很迷人</strong>\n        <p>它讓人覺得自己很認真、很負責。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>將就感令人不安</strong>\n        <p>即使方案已足夠好，人仍可能怕自己之後後悔。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>搜尋成本不直觀</strong>\n        <p>花時間比較看起來像努力，卻不總是有回報。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"micro-note\">滿意化不是放棄思考，而是把思考放在最值錢的地方。</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"applications\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Applications</p>\n      <h2>把夠好門檻帶回工程與管理決策</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">對工程團隊來說，很多拖延其實不是缺能力，而是沒有先定出『可以開始』的門檻。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"example-grid\">\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>架構選型</strong>\n        <p>先找符合安全、效能與維運底線的方案，比一直等理想解法實際。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>文件品質</strong>\n        <p>先做到足以讓新人不迷路，比追一次寫到完美更常能真正發生。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example\">\n        <strong>產品迭代</strong>\n        <p>若版本可回收，先推夠好方案收真實回饋，常比紙上找最優更有效。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n      <li>想用滿意化，先把最低可接受標準寫出來，否則很容易退成隨便。</li>\n      <li>如果一個決策可逆又高頻，通常不值得為了理想最優耗掉太多前進時間。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"misreadings\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Misreadings</p>\n      <h2>三個常見誤讀</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">滿意化不是廉價妥協，而是有限理性條件下的實用策略。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"collocation-list\" aria-label=\"常見誤讀\">\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>夠好就是不專業</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>在高搜尋成本情境下，懂得設門檻反而更專業。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>任何事都該滿意化</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>高不可逆、高風險題目仍可能值得更嚴格搜尋。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"collocation-card\">\n        <div>\n          <strong>滿意化等於沒有標準</strong>\n          <span class=\"register-tag\">校正</span>\n        </div>\n        <p>相反地，它最需要清楚標準。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"questions\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Questions</p>\n      <h2>我是在追更好，還是在為了追最優而延誤真正重要的前進</h2>\n      </div>\n    <div class=\"prompt-grid\">\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>如果今天必須做決定，我的最低可接受門檻是什麼</strong>\n        <p>把門檻說出來通常就能縮短僵局。</p>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"prompt-card\">\n        <strong>再多找一輪，真的有很大機率找到顯著更好解嗎</strong>\n        <p>若沒有，搜尋本身可能已不值。</p>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"template-note\">\n      <strong>延伸路線</strong>\n      <p>延伸閱讀可接 bounded rationality、search cost 與 decision strategy。</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\" id=\"sources\">\n    <div class=\"section-heading\">\n      <p class=\"section-label\">Sources</p>\n      <h2>來源與整理方式</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-lede\">這一頁以 satisficing 為主，再把概念帶回工程決策、工具選型與有限資源管理。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"source-grid\">\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>主概念</strong>\n        <p>Satisficing 條目整理了在有限理性條件下選擇夠好方案的概念。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Satisficing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Satisficing</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>理論背景</strong>\n        <p>Bounded rationality 可作為背景，理解為何現實決策常不追求全域最優。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bounded_rationality\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Bounded Rationality</a>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"source-card\">\n        <strong>相鄰概念</strong>\n        <p>Search cost 條目有助於理解繼續找更好選項本身為何也是成本。</p>\n        <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Search_cost\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Search Cost</a>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"chapter\">\n    <div class=\"reference-box\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"section-label\">Reference</p>\n        <h2>下一步</h2>\n        <p>讀完後可以挑一個你拖很久的選擇，先寫出『夠好就能前進』的三條門檻。</p>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"reference-link\" href=\"../knowledge-topic-template.html\">打開模板</a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</article>"
  }
}
